cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Agent Security Threat Model
message: If you use or adapt this work, please cite it.
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Peseckis
    given-names: Larry
version: v0.3
date-released: 2026-06-16
license: CC-BY-4.0
url: https://github.com/larrypeseckis/agent-security-threat-model
repository-code: https://github.com/larrypeseckis/agent-security-threat-model
abstract: >-
  A practical threat model for AI agents that use tools, browsers, files,
  terminals, APIs, and cloud resources. Organized around trust boundaries and
  mapped to the OWASP Top 10 for Agentic Applications and the OWASP Top 10 for
  LLM Applications, with a threat-to-boundary-to-control matrix and a
  pre-deployment review checklist.
keywords:
  - threat-model
  - ai-security
  - agent-security
  - prompt-injection
  - tool-use
  - least-privilege
  - owasp-asi
